.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH devin-auth 1  "auth " 
.SH NAME
devin\-auth \- Authentication related commands
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdevin auth\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Authentication related commands
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
devin\-auth\-login(1)
Log in to Windsurf
.TP
devin\-auth\-logout(1)
Log out and remove stored credentials
.TP
devin\-auth\-status(1)
Check authentication status
.TP
devin\-auth\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
